MID_支援_オボロ_ベルカ_Ａ: $t1$Wmオボロ|7$Wmベルカ|3$w0|$Wsベルカ|$WaOboro, may I see you for a bit?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Belka...?!$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|There's no need to be on guard...$k$p...I'm ready to properly\nexplain everything to you.$k$pSo that you can put your\nthoughts and emotions in order.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|...?$k$pWhat do you mean?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|I'm telling you everything\nyou've wanted to know.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Huh?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaAt the time, I was an orphan,\ncompletely alone. A man took me in.$k$pHe controlled an underground assassination\norganization. Even though he adopted me,$k$phe never treated me or raised\nme lovingly, like a real daughter.$k$p$E怒,|The only thing I learned from\nhim were killing techniques.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa…………$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaOn that day, after he had finished his\nwork and returned to camp, he was$k$pgrumbling about stuff and was\nin a bad mood. That day's target$k$pwasn't very important or lucrative.\nIt was just some boring night burglary-$k$ptype stuff.$k$pI only remember two things he was\ncomplaining about. The first was...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|That day... That man...\nMy parents?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes. He said he had attacked a\nclothing merchant convoy that$k$pwas heading to a Nohrian camp.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|Why...?!$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|Your parents' store... It apparently\nwas making quite a lot of money.$k$pIt had connections with the Hoshidan\nnobility... They'd held some power.$k$pAn influential person on the\nNohrian side made them a target.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Kuh...! Mother, Father...!!!$k$pUnforgivable!!$k$pI cannot forgive your\nadopted father for this!!$k$pThis man... Where is he now...?!$k$pI must find him!!$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|...That's impossible.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaWhy? If you're thinking of\nhiding him from me, then...$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|He's already dead.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|What...?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|I have already killed him.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|What... What are you saying?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$WaOnce I had grown old enough,\nand possessed enough valuable$k$pexperience that I could use...\nAn order had come down to me personally.$k$p$Eキメ,|It was...to kill him.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|And then..you killed him?\nYour foster father?!$k$pThe man who raised you,\neven for a little while?!?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes.$k$pUsing everything that he had\ntaught me, without any hesitation.$k$pThese kinds of situations are not\nat all uncommon in that world.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|Wh-what was the reason?\nWhy did you have to kill that man?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I had killed enough by that point that\nsuch information was unnecessary.$k$pAlmost all the veteran assassins simply\ndid their job, no questions asked...$k$pIn his final moments...he'd said that his\nactions had finally caught up with him...$k$pThat was the second thing\nhe was grumbling about...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Then...what that means...the revenge\nthat I've waited my whole life to carry out...$k$pWhat I savored for so long......$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E怒,|Yes. He is not in this world anymore.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|…………$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Please, put yourself at ease.\nYou can kill me, instead.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Wha...?$k$pNow, now just hold on...?!\nWhy would I...?$k$pWhy did you come to that conclusion?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I was the one who stole your\ntarget of revenge from you.$k$pThat's why you can hate me.$k$pThe detestation, languishing and\ndesperation in the depths of your mind...$k$pThey need a new target to latch onto.$k$p$E通常,|You will not be able to bear\nthe burden otherwise...$k$pI may be the only appropriate target now.$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Alright, then. Come at me!$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa...Please stop.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E苦,|Why? Do you not hate me with\nevery shred of your being?$k\n$Wsオボロ|$Wa$E怒,汗|I burn with hatred. Of Nohr...\nOf that man who raised you...of you...$k$pBut the only thing that hatred creates is\nnew hatred... I understand this very well.$k$p$E怒,|After all, that is....$k$pThat is what resulted in that man's death,\nisn't it? This chain of hatred now only will$k$pcause misfortune and anguish.\nSo, shall you and I stop all this,$k$pand instead...walk together,\nhand in hand?$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa$E通常,|Oboro...$k\n$Wsオボロ|$WaIn addition, you...are also a\nfellow victim. Of that man.$k$pThat's why, I shall take a new vow.$k$pThat I shall fight with my Nohrian comrades,\nhand in hand, to create...a world of peace.$k\n$Wsベルカ|$Wa…………$k$p$Eキメ,|I see. I understand...$k
